A Rendezvous in Averoigne is a collection of science fiction , fantasy and horror stories by author Clark Ashton Smith . It was released in 1988 by Arkham House in an edition of 5,025 copies . The collection contains stories from Smith 's major story cycles of Averoigne , Hyperborea , Poseidonis , Xiccarph , and Zothique . 2nd printing , 2003 - ( no print numbers given ) . Jaffery , Sheldon ( 1989 ) . The Arkham House Companion . Mercer Island , WA : Starmont House , Inc. , 142 . Chalker , Jack L . ; Mark Owings ( 1998 ) . The Science - Fantasy Publishers : A Bibliographic History , 1923 - 1998 . Westminster , MD and Baltimore : Mirage Press , Ltd. , 56 - 57 . Joshi , S.T. ( 1999 ) . Sixty Years of Arkham House : A History and Bibliography . Sauk City , WI : Arkham House , 157 - 158 . Nielsen , Leon ( 2004 ) . Arkham House Books : A Collector 's Guide . Jefferson , NC and London : McFarland & Company , Inc. , 134 , 147 . 